{"tid":2441822,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國之聲：微軟電郵系統被中國政府支持的Hafnium入侵　德國證實6聯邦政府機關受害","createTime":"2021-03-11T03:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T03:18:31.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"88e6e8bdd369185993c4d4fbf71a38b8a217ee91","tid":2441822,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:11:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210310/WJCYNSNLHNC2PGZ2E7IK6FIU4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210310%2FWJCYNSNLHNC2PGZ2E7IK6FIU4U%2F&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=6a5cb120\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210310%2FWJCYNSNLHNC2PGZ2E7IK6FIU4U%2F&h=48026ad3\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210310/WJCYNSNLHNC2PGZ2E7IK6FIU4U/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n德國之聲中文網報導，微軟（Microsoft）2日表示，受中國政府支持的駭客團體Hafnium利用Exchange 的伺服器軟體漏洞，來入侵竊取用戶資料，攻擊目標主要鎖定美國的傳染病研究機構、大學、國防承包商、法律事務所、智庫和非政府組織（NGO）等。<br />\n歐洲銀行管理局（European Banking Authority）7日深夜也發布聲明，證實電郵系統遭到駭客攻擊，且為預防起見已將電郵系統離線。<br />\n德國聯邦資訊安全局並未透露受到波及的聯邦政府機關名單，但表示接獲境內通報Exchange遭駭客入侵的案件持續增加，因此建議用戶盡速安裝微軟提供的安全更新。<br />\n德國《世界報》（Die Welt）周一（3/8）報導，根據美國資安公司Rapid7分析，Exchange軟體遭遇的這波駭客攻擊，美國以外德國是受災最嚴重的國家。<br />\n德國聯邦資訊安全局上周已將威脅等級上調為最嚴重的「紅色警戒」。並已用傳統郵寄通知受害企業建議的因應措施，目前已有超過9000家德國企業接獲相關通知，但實際受害戶數恐怕遠更高。（中央社）"},{"pid":"b0839c1f837ea0701cdbbf46ef385e6299d38413","tid":2441822,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"都被人掟火魔，點會係磨菇"},{"pid":"dd4c8df50776b7187e6161b127dd1d6ba360c59e","tid":2441822,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"終国自主研發疫苗又成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636fb118639c91181691932f1a2b7af60a58f18b","tid":2441822,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T03:18:31.000Z","msg":"復必泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}